Dialogue: 3,0:01:47.43,0:01:57.41,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Na dlanovima pahulje koje sipaju sa neba,
Dialogue: 4,0:01:57.74,0:02:08.10,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}nikada ih neću ispustiti iz zagrljaja.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.94,0:02:18.91,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Već sam imala snage
